#: ../../../migrating.rst:614
msgid ""
"Most of the model methods that previously edited the model in-place have "
"been updated to no longer do this. Instead, these methods will now return a "
"new instance of the newly updated model. This has been done to avoid the "
"library running into race conditions between in-place edits and gateway "
"events on model updates. See :issue:`4098` for more information."
