#: ../../../migrating.rst:889
msgid ""
"Originally, embeds used a special sentinel to denote emptiness or remove an "
"attribute from display. The ``Embed.Empty`` sentinel was made when Discord's "
"embed design was in a nebulous state of flux. Since then, the embed design "
"has stabilised and thus the sentinel is seen as legacy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../migrating.rst:891
msgid "Therefore, ``Embed.Empty`` has been removed in favour of ``None``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../migrating.rst:893
msgid ""
"Additionally, ``Embed.__eq__`` has been implemented thus embeds becoming "
"unhashable (e.g. using them in sets or dict keys)."
msgstr ""

